  <summary date="2019-03-08T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Building Success for Youth ChalleNGe Act

This bill authorizes the federal government and state, tribal, county, and local governments to transfer excess equipment and facilities to the National Guard for purposes of the Youth Challenge Program, which seeks to improve life skills and employment potential of at-risk youth.</summary>
